description:
Welcome to the placeholder October SWmobile tech talk event.

We're trying to get back to a regular monthly cadence with the meetups however if we're unable to source a speakers/venue we'll convert this into an informal social. If you are keen to speak please fill in the CFP form[ http://cfp.swmobile.org](http://cfp.swmobile.org)

Looking forward to seeing you there!

**Talks**

* TBC

**Timings:**
18:30 Doors open, Food (typically pizza with veg and vegan options) available & drink
19:00 Intro and talks
19:45 Break
20:00 talks
20:45 Finish (tidy up)
21:00 Continue the conversation at nearby pub (TBC)

See you there!
title: October Tech Talk Night
